title: CMakeLists: Remove -march=native options in case of cross compilation
message:
CMakeLists: Remove -march=native options in case of cross compilation

This option can break cross-compilations of the program

In my test yocto CFLAGS -march and -mtune were ignored due to
the -march=native.
